posting_body: ['The Sinclair', '414 SW Hayworth DR, Port Orchard, WA, 98367', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 95', 'OR Text', '95', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Step Into The Sinclair!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 968 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Step into The Sinclair: The stuff that life is made of.', 'Our newly built vintage chic community in Port Orchard presents 1, 2 & 3 bedroom homes.', 'Each private apartment provides well-organized space and storage options along with immaculate, stylish appliances and designer fixtures and lighting.', 'Relax outside on your private deck or patio with community, pool and wooded views.', 'Upgrade features available including plank flooring and advanced connectivity.', 'Experience our club house, outdoor grills, playgrounds, fitness center and convenient car detailing area.', 'Don’t wait, Contact The Sinclair today!', 'Features', '- Full Size Washer/Dryer in Home', '- Internet/Cable Ready', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Extra Storage', '- Efficient Appliances', '- Dishwasher', 'Community Amenities', '- Pet Friendly', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Walking Trails', '- EV Charging Stations', '- Amazon Lockers', '- Secured Garages', '- Off Street Parking', '- Car Detailing Area', '- Recycling', '- Business Center', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- High Speed Internet', '- Valet Trash Service', '- Resident Lounge', '- On-Site Management', '- 24/7 Fitness Center', '- Seasonal Heated Pool', '- Playground', '- Covered Carports', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 8:00AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday-Sunday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats & Dogs allowed.', '2 pets per household.', 'One-time $600 non-refundable pet fee & additional $200 for 2nd pet.', 'Pet rent is $25 a month and $45 monthly for two', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5x rent to gross income ratio (household)', 's1qOIeYZmm9']
